Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也是美好的一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今年的最后 还是要做「那个」才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做「那个」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的一年要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝…这么一想确实会让人感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心中的美好是永远都不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 今天是24月31日 天晴 有时下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来到AQUA后的第二个除夕夜就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 可是空气很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在AQUA度过的第二个春夏秋冬里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:01:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所度过的每一天都如同宝物般闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 在地球上圣诞节是大家一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.92,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕则是与家人一起过的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新威尼斯却相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟家人一起过圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.26,0:01:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟朋友一起过除夕才是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天我们要去圣马可广场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起过除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.97,0:01:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我也好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子好慢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏人家这么早来帮艾莉西亚小姐占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晓先生 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会 快请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已为艾莉西亚小姐占好座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯的除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全城的人都会聚集到圣马可广场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要活动是新年倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一直到新年日出之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们都会为庆祝新年而彻夜狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在这个时候 大家才会不拘礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是喧闹而盛大的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让小爱也来这里看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我来看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才好像听到小爱的声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 我来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.93,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 纯白的早晨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～ 艾莉西亚前辈知道小爱要来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:05:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想给灯里一个惊喜 就没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟艾莉西亚也是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你姐姐他们呢？是一起来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐会在天亮的时候来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐夫笃井因为工作关系要明天下午才来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就能一起过除夕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鬓子 这个小不点女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 你是气候调节员晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是空中邮递员伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你认识我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从灯里的邮件里知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里 晓先生很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气候调节员为了让AQUA的人们过得舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在浮岛上每日奋战着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 气候调节员是正义的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你在哥哥面前总是抬不起头来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为欠哥哥的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬓子啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个可爱的孩子的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可爱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到个可爱的女朋友了嘛 弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 是晓先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就找到第三个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 找到…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了灯里邮件中出现的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸出来好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用新威尼斯玻璃制作的豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆子象征着财富 据说能带来幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上的意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有年末一定要吃豆子料理的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这个城市也继承了那个传统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过玻璃做的豆子不能吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是观光的礼物啦 很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要弄丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}别掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？是不是有种幸福将要来临的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作你跟我任性的弟弟这么要好的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么要好啊…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…叔叔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走一步了 再会了 淑女们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好像比你更帅气…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大家都到齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈～ 晚安～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟大家一起过除夕 就跑来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么远的距离 你可真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 这孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是鬼教官晃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就找到第四个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 蓝华！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里！你到底给小爱写的什么邮件啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的…就是一般的邮件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是阿鲁先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 初次见面 我就是重力调节员阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…重力调节员就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地下调节重力的工作…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有一件事很难启齿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对蓝华到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！到此为止！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 灯里 那孩子会不会太兴奋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 亚利亚社长 飞高高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}飞啊飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能够与原本只能从我的邮件中认识的人们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}飞啊飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像与小说中的登场人物直接见面了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件很让人高兴的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您最近安好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你这么有精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 大家都到齐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还是像以前这么要好 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是祖母吗 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是第六个人了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 是位可爱的小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是灯里的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她是从地球来的 叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖母 请来这边坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鬓子 那位贵妇人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一位是创立了亚利亚公司的大前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…把亚利亚社长跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足迹一直延伸到这里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信件真的能穿越时空 传达心意的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说猫是连接过去和未来的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的…难道是以前的AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议…总觉得…有种熟悉的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…虽然是完全不了解的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 我受到AQUA的欢迎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定是这样的 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是让人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西在发光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…果然破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西都掉出去了 什么时候破的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说 只要顺着这些光走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能回到原来的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！是光的路标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们一边捡一边回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里前辈她们好慢啊 不会出什么事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们一定是到处去逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 灯里 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们跑哪里去了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊？AQUA不就是这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 小爱 你带了什么可以扔的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以扔的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新威尼斯除夕最盛大的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在新年的凌晨零点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起用力把什么东西扔向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是去年使用过的东西 什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里要扔什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们领航员都是扔这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我…扔这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个缎带是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 上次来的时候系的缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要来新威尼斯 所以就系上它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？很有纪念意义的缎带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要开始倒数了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 新年的庆贺语是AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGURI…BUON ANNO？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 AUGURI是祝贺的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BUON ANNO则是新年快乐的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年真的发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的邂逅 和独一无二的美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到这像宝物一样闪闪发光的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点让人感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让…让人害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个奢侈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的奢侈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}dieci(10)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}nove(9)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}otto(8)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sette(7)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sei(6)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}cinque(5)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}quattro(4)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}tre(3)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}due(2)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}uno(1)！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AUGURI BUON ANNO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 灯里 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就睡着了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是刚刚才醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 看看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我一坐下这孩子就会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 她的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫做 AQUA（水星）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 AQUA真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟这孩子一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的AQUA的新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 AQUA 太阳要升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳的光芒让人感觉到了温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连内心深处也被温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今年也是美好的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今年也会为了成为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独当一面的领航员而努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝华 这种话应该跟我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用全身去感受阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异常耀眼而崭新的 纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是个崭新的 暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白的一年的初始之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以后的世界将被染成什么样的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 爱 我们该回酒店了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好地睡一觉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为下午还要跟笃井姐夫会合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱跟她姐姐看起来很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈跟小爱的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在她来水星做新婚旅行的时候见过的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宝贝比照相的时候长大了许多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能带着孩子一起来 真是令人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没想到再次相会时彼此的家人都增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…彼此？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯里…AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亚前辈 AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是 要请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对创造了这个美好的星球的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对在这美好的星球上共度时光的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也对这个美好的星球 AQUA…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是对将要邂逅的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心满怀感激之情
