Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.93,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:56.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}You make me smile いつもよりも 特別なその笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:03.10,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}切なさもきっと 消えてくの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:11.47,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Every Day こんな日々が 想い出に変わっても
