Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.87,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}just for you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:05:01.39,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}轻轻地 隐约传来 断续的涛声 你听！
